this-dark-world\">Source</a></td></tr>\n		<tr><td>Bye Bye Blackbird</td> <td>Credits</td> <td>Not Found</td></tr>\n		<tr><td>And Then We Were One</td> <td>Extra Room</td> <td><a href=\"http://eyeshalfclosed.bandcamp.com/track/and-then-we-were-one\">Source</a></td></tr>\n		<tr><td><hr></td></tr>\n		<tr><td>thiswillmakeyoucry</td> <td>Extra Ending</td> <td><a href=\"http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=a_Am4cHMBKM\">Source</a></td></tr>\n		</tbody></table>\n	</div>\n</div>\";s:6:\"format\";s:9:\"full_html\";s:10:\"substitute\";i:1;}','a:0:{}','a:1:{s:8:\"settings\";N;}','a:0:{}','a:0:{}',0,'a:0:{}','1b347ae9-8d5c-4fdd-b51b-8c326d910166'),(116,32,'bottom','custom','custom',1,'a:0:{}','a:5:{s:11:\"admin_title\";s:6:\"Footer\";s:5:\"title\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"body\";s:476:\"<div class = \"game_general_footer_wrapper\">\n	<ul class = \"list\">\n		<li class = \"no_1 item first\">\n			<a class = \"link\" href = \"57\">Contact</a>\n		</li>\n		<li class = \"no_2 item\">\n			<a class = \"link\" href = \"5\">Main page</a>\n		</li>\n		<li class = \"no_4 item\">\n			<a class = \"link\" href = \"http://vgperson.tumblr.com\">News</a>\n		</li>\n		<li class = \"no_5 item last\">\n			<a class = \"link\" href = \"https://github.com/Trelil/VGP-SiteProject\">Page creators</a>\n		</li>\n	</ul>\n</div>\";s:6:\"format\";s:9:\"full_html\";s:10:\"substitute\";i:1;}','a:0:{}','a:1:{s:8:\"settings\";N;}','a:0:{}','a:0:{}',0,'a:0:{}','a8c38bdc-b7c7-498e-a254-405e8b7871df'),(117,33,'top','custom','custom',1,'a:0:{}','a:5:{s:11:\"admin_title\";s:6:\"Header\";s:5:\"title\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"body\";s:707:\"<img class = \"game_general_background\" src = \"../files/thegraygarden/background.png\" alt = \"\" />\n<div class = \"game_general_header_wrapper\">\n	<h1 class = \"header\">\n		VGPerson\n	</h1>\n	<nav class = \"menu\">\n		<ul class = \"list\">\n			<li class = \"no_1 item first\">\n				<a class = \"link\" href = \"5\">Main</a>\n			</li>\n			<li class = \"no_2 item\">\n				<a class = \"link\" href = \"4\">Lyrics</a>\n			</li>\n			<li class = \"no_3 item\">\n				<a class = \"link\" href = \"1\">Games</a>\n			</li>\n			<li class = \"no_4 item last\">\n				<a class = \"link\" href = \"57\">About</a>\n			</li>\n		</ul>\n	</nav>\n	<h3 class = \"sub_header\">\n		The gray garden\n	</h3>\n	<link rel = \"stylesheet\" href = \"../files/game_general_page_style.css\" />\n</div>\";s:6:\"format\";s:9:\"full_html\";s:10:\"substitute\";i:1;}','a:0:{}','a:1:{s:8:\"settings\";N;}','a:0:{}','a:0:{}',0,'a:0:{}','8b3fc273-60e1-464b-85cb-9df206d7650c'),(118,33,'left','custom','custom',1,'a:0:{}','a:5:{s:11:\"admin_title\";s:11:\"Left column\";s:5:\"title\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"body\";s:804:\"<div class = \"game_general_left_column_wrapper\">\n	<div class = \"cover_image\">\n		<img src = \"../files/thegraygarden/cover.png\" class = \"image\" alt = \"Game cover image.\" />\n	</div>\n	<div class = \"download_section\">\n		<a href = \"../files/thegraygarden/game.zip\" class = \"download button\">\n			Download game\n		</a>\n	</div>\n	<ul class = \"list\">\n		<li class = \"no_1 item first\">\n			<img src = \"../files/thegraygarden/screenshot_0.png\" class = \"screenshot image\" alt = \"Screenshot image.\" />\n		</li>\n		<li class = \"no_2 item\">\n			<img src = \"../files/thegraygarden/screenshot_1.png\" class = \"screenshot image\" alt = \"Screenshot image.\" />\n		</li>\n		<li class = \"no_3 item last\">\n			<img src = \"../files/thegraygarden/screenshot_2.png\" class = \"screenshot image\" alt = \"Screenshot image.\" />\n		</li>\n	</ul>\n</div>\";s:6:\"format\";s:9:\"full_html\";s:10:\"substitute\";i:1;}','a:0:{}','a:1:{s:8:\"settings\";N;}','a:0:{}','a:0:{}',0,'a:0:{}','287de442-6682-4145-9623-351f7b0bdddd'),(119,33,'right','custom','custom',1,'a:0:{}','a:5:{s:11:\"admin_title\";s:12:\"Right column\";s:5:\"title\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"body\";s:10185:\"<div class = \"game_general_right_column_wrapper\">\n	<div class = \"description\">\n		<p>\n			<strong>The Gray Garden</strong> is a pseudo-RPG with a heavy story focus,\n			made by Mogeko (site name Deep-Sea Prisoner) in RPG Maker 2000.\n		</p>\n		<p>\n			The Gray Garden: a world where angels and demons live in harmony.\n			Yosafire, a demon who likes flowers, enjoys a carefree life with her friends.\n			Then one day, a mysterious bat appears in the garden...\n		</p>\n		<p>\n			<strong>Warning:</strong> There are a number of depictions of violence and gore throughout the game.\n			However, none of it is presented in a \"startling\" way, and nothing too detailed is shown graphics-wise.\n		</p>\n	</div>\n	<div class = \"bonus hide\">\n<div class = \'toggle-button\' onclick = \"var a = document.getElementsByClassName(\'bonus\')[0]; if(a.classList.contains(\'hide\')){a.classList.remove(\'hide\');}else{a.classList.add(\'hide\');}\">Toggle</div>\n		<h2>Extras</h2>\n		<p>\n			The game is very straightfoward, but there are some things you might miss. (Spoiler warning!)\n		</p>\n		<h3>\n			Bad End 1\n		</h3>\n		<p>\n			During the part in Flame Town where Emalf chases you,\n			one of the wrong turns will lead to a dead end where he catches you.\n		</p>\n		<h3>\n			Bad End 2\n		</h3>\n		<p>\n			Lose the first fight against Poemi in the Wastelands.\n		</p>\n		<h3>\n			Bad End 3\n		</h3>\n		<p>\n			When Macarona finds Rawberry in the village, choose \"Yaaaaaaaaaah!!!\"\n		</p>\n		<h3>\n			Normal End\n		</h3>\n		<p>\n			Lose to the final boss (the actual fight).\n		</p>\n		<h3>\n			Radio Wave\n		</h3>\n		<p>\n			After beating the final boss, go to the coast to get this. It unlocks a thing in the bonus room.\n		</p>\n		<h3>\n			Second Playthrough\n		</h3>\n		<p>\n			There are a few minor bonuses on your second playthrough.\n			Whether they\'re worth actually playing again for is... up to you, I suppose.\n		</p>\n		<h4>\n			Apples\n		</h4>\n		<p>\n			You don\'t need to collect any apples in Apple Park to proceed. Uh, thanks? ...How does that work?\n		</p>\n		<h4>\n			666 Ticket\n		</h4>\n		<p>\n			Froze\'s house will contain a 666 Ticket, which summons the Passing Demon to help in battle.\n		</p>\n		<h4>\n			Prosciutto Equipment\n		</h4>\n		<p>\n			A side area in Evening Forest formerly blocked by plants will be open.\n			A Mogeko there will make Yosafire max level and give her the overpowered Prosciutto equipment.\n		</p>\n		<h4>\n			???\n		</h4>\n		<p>\n			The ??? video is different depending on if you view it right after beating the game the first time,\n			or if you view it after returning the bonus room on a second playthrough.\n			(Just starting a second loop and going to the door in Yosafire\'s house ASAP will work.)\n		</p>\n		<h2>\n			Garden Gray The\n		</h2>\n		<p>\n			Mogeko released <a href = \"http://www.mediafire.com/?q1bj531nc9vozud\">Garden Gray The 0.00</a> for April Fools\' Day 2014. (Mac version at same link)\n			It\'s about ten minutes long and quite silly. And it shouldn\'t really spoil the main game at all.\n		</p>\n	</div>\n	<div class = \"music hide\">\n<div class = \'toggle-button\' onclick = \"var a = document.getElementsByClassName(\'music\')[0]; if(a.classList.contains(\'hide\')){a.classList.remove(\'hide\');}else{a.classList.add(\'hide\');}\">Toggle</div>\n		<h2>Music</h2>\n		<p>\n			Below is a list of all the songs used in the game.\n			I don\'t have individual source links, but all songs can be found in the Music folder.\n			There are <strong>definite spoilers</strong> for their usage, so don\'t look until you\'ve beaten the game!\n		</p>\n		<p>\n			For clarification, the filename titles are the titles given by the original sites, so they aren\'t based on the game.\n			The \"Usage\" names are descriptions I made up based on where they\'re used - Mogeko had no part in deciding those.\n		</p>\n		<table>\n		<tbody><tr><td><b>Sorted Chronologically</b><br></td></tr>\n		<tr><td><b>Filename</b></td> <td><b>Usage</b></td> <td><b>Source</b></td></tr>\n		<tr><td>Amor Kana_SoaringYonder(MusicBox)</td> <td>Title / A Nice Old Man</td> <td>Amor Kana</td></tr>\n		<tr><td>CAMeLIA